
QR Code Web Solution 🔗📱


🚀 Project Overview
This is my first client project as a Software Engineer—a simple yet powerful solution that allows users to scan a QR code and instantly open a web page displaying:

🗺️ Shop Location

📞 Owner Contact Details

🔗 Social Media Links

Designed to help shop owners create a quick and accessible digital identity for their business.

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3

QR Code Integration

✨ Key Features
✅ Scan QR code to access shop details
✅ Mobile-responsive design
✅ Contact info, map location, and social media links in one place
✅ Lightweight and fast-loading

📸 How It Works
Generate or scan the QR code.

The QR code opens the web page.

The user can view shop location, contact details, and social media links instantly.

🌐 Demo
👉 https://aakib-123.github.io/zcalocation/

